# ZenithSpectra — environment templates (monorepo uses PER-APP env files)
#
# Copy each per-app template to ".env" in its app directory:
#   backend/.env.example   ->  backend/.env         (FastAPI: DB, LLM provider/model, CORS, ingestion)
#   frontend/.env.example  ->  frontend/.env.local  (Next.js: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL)
#
# Those per-app files are the authoritative variable lists. Do NOT duplicate
# concrete values here — the old duplicate block caused dev/prod LLM model drift.
